                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Dependability</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  We show up when we say we will. Our solutions work the first time. When you need locksmith service in Anderson, you can count on us.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gold-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Honest Work</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  No upselling, no surprise charges, no runaround. We tell you what needs to be done, what it'll cost, and why. Simple as that.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gold-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Real Experience</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Nine years of residential, commercial, and automotive locksmith work. We've seen most situations before, and we know how to handle them.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gold-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Local Accountability</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  We live here. Our kids go to school here. We shop at the same stores you do. That local accountability shapes how we do business.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Why Choose Us -->
          <div class="mb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal-900 to-charcoal-800 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-12 text-center">Why Choose {companyConfig.name}?</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
              <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-400 to-gold-500 text-charcoal-900">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
